headline: 1 Magnificent High-Yield Dividend Stock Down 50% to Buy and Hold Forever
summary: Investors have moved from overenthusiastic to overly pessimistic.  Wall Street has a habit of moving between extremes, often swinging from shocking enthusiasm to despondent pessimism.  It's down more than 50% from its peak, and long-term income investors should probably do a deep dive, because the service on offer is vital to modern life.
